that area? what kind of resistance are in that place???"

> answering to Cryotek said"Still I have to pick up... that thing but I need
> some totally loyal troops in good shape... Tell me about those 
> arrangements"

<NEW>

Cyclonus left to take care of things inside of the base, leaving
Hydras to talk with Cryotek.

"Loyalty is a valubale commodity noble student." Cryotek said over the
radio as he chuckled. "The arrangements have already been made. I have
sent . . . others to examine the ship, the possible base." There was
another chuckle, "I believe they wanted the base more than you did.
Although I do believe that they have ran into a bit of resistance."

Cyclonus' voice cut in, "Sir. Terrorsaur, one of your soldiers is not
with us." There was a pause as if Cyclonus was confiring with someone
else. "The reports are saying that he has been missing since we came
from your old base. When most of us left, it seems that somehow he did
not make the trip."

"He's gone sir."
